            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-f09fcd twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section  2.  Information about the Mission of Project Gutenberg-tm</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/17f7f7f28f29cca2/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/17f7f7f28f29cca2/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-f09fcd twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-6b4cd0\"><p>Project Gutenberg-tm is synonymous with the free distribution of\nelectronic works in formats readable by the widest variety of computers\nincluding obsolete, old, middle-aged and new computers.  It exists\nbecause of the efforts of hundreds of volunteers and donations from\npeople in all walks of life.</p></div>"
