            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/17f7f7f28f29cca2/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-f09fcd twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-6b4cd0\"><p>For additional contact information:<br>\n\n     Dr. Gregory B. Newby<br>\n\n     Chief Executive and Director<br>\n\n     gbnewby@pglaf.org<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/17f7f7f28f29cca2/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/17f7f7f28f29cca2/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-f09fcd twpub-17f7f7f28f29cca2-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
